# Supabase – same project as the web app (use same URL and anon key from the dashboard)
# Session is persisted with expo-sqlite localStorage (app sandbox, survives restarts).
# Required: the app throws at startup if either variable is missing (fail-fast).
# Copy to .env and set real values. Never commit .env.
#
# EAS Build (profil production / Play Store / App Store) :
# Définir les MÊMES clés sur https://expo.dev → Projet → Environment variables
# (profil production), sinon le bundle n’embarque pas Supabase. Identiques au site web.
#
# Dashboard: add mobile redirect URLs + email template notes → docs/SUPABASE_MAGIC_LINK_AND_REDIRECTS.md
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
